REFERENCE           MENU_PRESTIGE_MODE_DESC_1
LANG_SPANISH        "YOU WILL START OVER AT LEVEL 1 HAVING GAINED A BIT OF PRESTIGE BUT YOU WILL KEEP ALL OF YOUR PROGRESS FOR CAMO, WEAPON LEVELS AND CHALLENGES.\N\NIN EXCHANGE YOU CAN PERMANENTLY UNLOCK AN ITEM AND\NCHOOSE ONE OF THREE PRESTIGE AWARDS:\N \N1. AN EXTRA CLASS SLOT.\N2. OPTION TO REFUND UNLOCK TOKENS ANYTIME.\N3. OPTION RESET ALL OF YOUR STATS AND PROGRESS."

REFERENCE           MENU_PRESTIGE_MODE_DESC_2
